<i>I found that town</i>

793
00:51:12,980 --> 00:51:17,480
<i>The one from dreams, I found that town</i>

794
00:51:17,646 --> 00:51:21,855
<i>Now with you, I feel home bound</i>

795
00:51:21,980 --> 00:51:24,313
<i>A sky</i>

796
00:51:24,396 --> 00:51:26,646
<i>My heart's a sky so wide</i>

797
