<i>My head on your chest</i>

809
00:52:12,896 --> 00:52:17,105
<i>We live in a home that's small but best</i>

810
00:52:17,230 --> 00:52:21,855
<i>The world may fade or stay in view</i>

811
00:52:21,980 --> 00:52:26,438
<i>I only fear not holding you</i>

812
00:52:26,813 --> 00:52:29,146
<i>What was I without you?</i>

813
00:52:29,230 --> 00:52:31,771
<i>Why did I exist without you?</i>

814
00:52:31,855 --> 00:52:36,021
<i>These thoughts keep coming to me too</i>

815
00:52:36,355 --> 00:52:41,063
<i>Now you're my world, I agree</i>

816
00:52:41,480 --> 00:52:46,021
<i>What's wrong with me?</i>

817
