Everyone started laughing.

1654
01:48:42,063 --> 01:48:43,438
That day…

1655
01:48:45,521 --> 01:48:48,271
I felt like something
was wrong with me, you know.

1656
01:48:48,396 --> 01:48:49,438
No.

1657
