I get it. I've been through my share too.

1671
01:49:46,688 --> 01:49:48,396
I flunked interviews.

1672
01:49:48,771 --> 01:49:50,771
I've been the butt of jokes.

1673
01:49:52,813 --> 01:49:55,980
As a kid I had a huge crush
on "Silpa Setty,"

1674
