No.

1687
01:50:59,271 --> 01:51:01,105
It's us, guys.

1688
01:51:01,188 --> 01:51:02,105
It's us!

1689
01:51:02,188 --> 01:51:04,688
People from all over Asia-Pacific
are flying down to Mumbai.

1690
01:51:04,771 --> 01:51:07,021
It can't get any bigger than this. Yes!

1691
01:51:07,146 --> 01:51:09,771
And it's because of all of you,
your hard work.

1692
01:51:09,980 --> 01:51:13,063
But we've still got a lot to do.
Get ready, Shashank. Alright?

1693
01:51:13,146 --> 01:51:16,146
I don't want any complaints.
Everything has to be perfect.

1694
01:51:16,355 --> 01:51:17,313
Right?

1695
